Phillip Trent https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phillip_Trent 0 Phillip Trent (Oct 16, 1907, Wilkes-Barre, Pennsylvania–Jan 24, 2001, Englewood, New Jersey) was an American stage and film actor. He began his career on Broadway and starred in nine stage productions. He appeared in numerous films during the 1930s and 1940s. He also appeared as Clifford Jones.
